{"tid":2112840,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"數碼通執行董事及總裁葉安娜辭任","createTime":"2020-07-17T15:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T12:26:25.000Z","uid":64918,"like":71,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"dadd7cb8cdace471368abf2f02bd20487941a241","tid":2112840,"uid":64918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:31:50.000Z","msg":"數碼通公布，葉安娜已辭任公司執行董事及總裁職務，以尋求其他事業發展。辭任將於下月17日起生效，其後將留任董事會顧問一段時間，以協助交接職務。<br />\n<br />\n公司指，現正物色合適人選以委任為公司總裁。<br />\n<br />\n公告又指，副主席及非執行董事馮玉麟將調任為公司執行董事，於過渡期間，他與現任高級管理團隊將一同負責葉安娜的職務並領導公司。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538382-20200717.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538382-20200717.htm&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpfaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=dfe1890d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538382-20200717.htm&h=65514ca1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538382-20200717.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n作為 CEO, 最後 5G 成功 採用 Ericsson , 隻鑊咩晒上身, 都算係咁."},{"pid":"488bf78f893dd1b3c22b8b2427adf7d630d5957a","tid":2112840,"uid":64918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:41:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"51fe854a1b18b9fbbedbbec5589b0cd505dbe1de","tid":2112840,"uid":42804,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T16:31:43.000Z","msg":"如果下一任係紅底就<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7885ed27ed93fac13e07d53ec2f08c2323efd6f8","tid":2112840,"uid":64918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"51fe854a1b18b9fbbedbbec5589b0cd505dbe1de","tid":2112840,"uid":42804,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T16:31:43.000Z","msg":"如果下一任係紅底就<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"